videos.description: Marvin Bagley III heads to the locker room with an apparent hand injury in the opening minutes against Miami.
videos.headline: Duke's Bagley III injured early against Miami

videos.description: Chris Lykes dances after driving through two defenders to drill a tough layup off the glass.
videos.headline: Miami's Lykes celebrates after tough layup

videos.description: Anthony Lawrence II strips Duke's Marvin Bagley III and takes it all the way home for an easy layup.
videos.headline: Bagley III's turnover leads to Miami layup

videos.description: Miami's Wendell Carter Jr. swats Gary Trent Jr.'s shot with authority and sends it out of bounds.
videos.headline: Carter Jr. emphatically blocks shot

videos.description: Dewan Huell gets the offensive rebound and quickly takes it to the rim for a one-handed flush.
videos.headline: Huell capitalizes on rebound

videos.description: Lonnie Walker IV anticipates Grayson Allen's pass and sends it to a wide-open Bruce Brown Jr. who takes it down the court for a two-handed jam.
videos.headline: Allen turnover becomes Miami dunk

videos.description: Grayson Allen dives to save the ball in the final seconds of the first half and tosses it up to Gary Trent Jr. who drills a 3-pointer at the buzzer.
videos.headline: Trent Jr. drains buzzer-beater

videos.description: Bruce Brown Jr. steals and passes to Anthony Lawrence II who gets the crowd going by draining a quick 3-pointer.
videos.headline: Lawrence II gets crowd fired up with 3-pointer

videos.description: Lonnie Walker IV steals and flushes a 3-pointer which fires the crowd including Jennifer Lopez and Alex Rodriguez.
videos.headline: A-Rod and J.Lo celebrate Miami 3-pointer

videos.description: Miami's Chris Lykes makes a 3-pointer over the out stretched hands of  Duke's Trevon Duval.
videos.headline: Lykes drills contested 3-pointer

videos.description: Ja'Quan Newton bounce passes to Dewan Huell who punishes the rim with a major dunk.
videos.headline: Newton connects with Huell for huge slam

videos.description: Duke's Marvin Bagley III banks in layup and gets fouled for a 3-point play.
videos.headline: Bagley III makes tough basket for and-1

videos.description: Wendell Carter Jr. fires up Duke's bench after making a layup to tie Miami.
videos.headline: Carter Jr layup pumps up the bench

videos.description: Wendell Carter Jr. blows past Miami defender to finish with a layup.
videos.headline: Carter Jr. bursts to the rim

videos.description: Gary Trent Jr. celebrates after drilling a 3-pointer to seal the deal for Duke.
videos.headline: Trent Jr. knocks down dagger 3-pointer

videos.description: Led by Gary Trent Jr.'s career-high 30 points, the No. 5 Blue Devils overcome a 13-point halftime deficit to beat the No. 25 Hurricanes 83-75.
videos.headline: Duke rallies to top Miami

videos.description: Grayson Allen steals, bursts down the court and soars to punish the rim with a two-handed flush.
videos.headline: Allen dunks with authority
